plate.name: [Pre-order] Phase One 65 Plate
plate.description:
Specs
The solder version plate would fit both the WK and WKL layout
The hot-swap WKL plate would only fit the hot-swap WKL PCB
The hot-swap WK plate would only fit the hot-swap WK PCB
Notes
If you choose a half plate, the Hot-swap PCB will not fit with the 3-pin switches perfectly, as some 3-pin switches might be easily pulled out when you are pulling out the keycaps.
